            For the Government to give a few million pounds to a company in such a situation would be like turning to a drowning man with a hundredweight of lead strapped
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_250wh' title='Col. 250WH &mdash; HC Deb 07 February 2001 vol 362 c250WH' name='column_250wh' href='#column_250wh' rel='bookmark'>250WH</a>
